{"tid":389454,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"CSL 搞$168無限上網","createTime":"2017-09-06T09:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T15:01:32.000Z","uid":731,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b72cf9aaa67f13c8a45704abae9bbab13795526","tid":389454,"uid":731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:31:19.000Z","msg":"今次真係會慢撚到仆街<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/3145/208866/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F3145%2F208866%2F1%2F&d=cjmf4A%2BpYGFx723OlEA3xf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=d0b42b3e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/3145/208866/1/</a><br />\n<br />\n5 人集氣，平均 $168.4 享真無限全速 4.5G 數據<br />\n想達至 $154 無限上網，需要有一個條件：就係要 5 人集氣。講到呢度，相信聰明的網友已經知道，版主想說的是多人共享 Plan。唔理係乜嘢 Plan，版主只係想同大家計下，到底成件事抵唔抵。先睇官網，可以見到而家 csl. 將「用量皇」服務，都加入到多人共享 Plan 度，而且仲要減左價，只要攜號上台申請 $558 的 10GB Plan，就可以另外加 $150 享有真‧無限上網。就咁都仲未叫最抵玩，既然有真‧無限上網，當然愈多人平分就愈抵玩，只要再加多 $116 (每張 $58)，就可以額外開多 2 張 SIM，即 total 5 張 SIM，5 個人共用，平均每個人 $168.4。"},{"pid":"439052b1320669b7a9fc97653565c498fbb5d8d9","tid":389454,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T09:38:35.000Z","msg":"岩岩先續左約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貴約黎架<br />\n屌你老母臭閪"},{"pid":"16053617f099f023e14ec229b286f656f2fa4ca0","tid":389454,"uid":25612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:49:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a541eed1df399d15e8dea6d01bafec953bf30878","tid":389454,"uid":126044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩先續左約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貴約黎架<br />\n屌你老母臭閪</blockquote><br />\n早兩三年賣到貴一貴又谷行廣告呃d傻西以為佢會特別快<br />\n<br />\n呃到7788就一野㩒低個價搶客<br />\n之個網速就攬炒<br />\n<br />\n我都係俾佢呃左既傻西之一<br />\n好撚後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\